---
title: Italian Herb Chicken Thighs and Pea Risotto with Spinach and Parmesan
description: Creamy risotto and cheesy baked chicken thighs are a match made in heaven in this classic, hearty dish. A little patience with the risotto is worth it to coax this time-honoured tradition into a luxurious meal!
